exbug-1.2.bin can be used, but the lowest level function to read a character
from the UART (ACIA) is at a different address than it is for exbug.bin
(which is exbug-1.1).

So you must recompile exorsim to intercept this address instead.

Robert Offner:
This is a minimalist version of exorsim. It is just for 6800 CPU and only for Exorset.